[8:41:19] EliteHunter_: @UberHaxorNova Start of the stream i saw that you had a problem with windows update again and complained about the auto updates again. I'm surprised you haven't searched how to disable it before. Here is how to; Write gpedit in start it will show gorup policy editor. Go into Computer Configuration > Administrative Templates > Windows Components > Windows Update. To the right you'll see a list where it'll say configure automatic updates. Double click it and select radio button "Disabled" on toplf
